      * Rebuttal for round 1: July 20-22, 2026<br>
      * Notification for round 1: August 6, 2026<br>
      * Submission deadline for round 2: Thursday, October 15, 2026<br>
      * Rebuttal for round 2: December 7-9, 2026<br>
      * Paper notification: Tuesday, December 22, 2026<br>
